# Exclude all data files (can be large), but keep docs and small samples.
# Note: to re-include a file in a subdir, the subdir itself must be re-included first.
*
!.gitignore
!README.md

# Re-include subdirectories so nested docs/samples below are reachable
!*/

# Within any subdirectory, exclude everything then keep only docs/small samples
*/**
!**/README.md
!**/samples.json
!**/samples/
!**/download.sh
!**/download_instructions.txt
